                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid_10">
                <section class="seniors-header">
                    <div class="grid_8">
                        <h1>S.A.F.E. - Self Defense Skills for Everyone</h1>
                        <p>We offer self defense classes for all levels.  Classes are grouped into youth only, seniors only, womens only, and co-ed classes.  
                        Our self defense classes focus on the physical, emotional and psychological aspects of an attack through a hands-on and
                            lecture combination that allows students to practice various self-defense techniques</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="coupon grid_4 primary-nav-button">
                        <a id="coupon-button" href="/home/free-coupon?src=self-defense" title="Print a coupon for our fitness classes & workout classes"
