                        <p>Statistics show that the greater number of defensive methods employed during an attack, the higher the chance of escape... S.A.F.E. teaches you 
                          the skills to handle various situations.  S.A.F.E. stands for "Self Defense Awareness Fundamentals for Everyone".  S.A.F.E. is an advanced, 
                          yet simple system designed for Crime Prevention, General Wellness, Personal Safety, and Self Defense.
                          </p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="clearfix">
                </div>
                <section class="seniors">
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <h2>Discover Your Strength - You Can Do This!</h2>
                        <p>We create an environment where you feel comfortable enough to challenge yourself
                            and discover your strength. You will learn to use your entire body, regardless of
                            your strength, size body type or level of fitness. Students of up to 81 years of
                            age have completed this course.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <div class="image-placeholder">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="clearfix">
                </div>
                <section class="seniors">
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <div class="image-placeholder">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <h2>Why Risk It?</h2>
                        <p>Our programs draw on years of experience in various types of self-defense and martial
                            arts. We will teach you the tactics and strategies that you need - to protect yourself
                            and those you love. Is it really worth it to get your training elsewhere? Don't
                            believe us - simply drop by.</p>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="clearfix">
                </div>
                <section class="seniors">
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <h2>Use Fear to Your Advantage</h2>
                        <p>Many people when in a self defense situation are overcome by fear. Our S.A.F.E. self defense program
                            teaches you how to turn your fear into effective self-defense energy.  
                            Ward off attackerss - protect yourself & loved ones - using new found self-defense energy.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid_6">
                        <div class="image-placeholder" style="">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
                <div class="clearfix">
                </div>
